  "name": "Astable Multivibrator",
  "lesson": {
    "title": "Astable Multivibrator",
    "description": "Classic two-transistor astable multivibrator: two NPN stages, two 47k base bias resistors, two 10uF cross-coupling capacitors, and mirrored LED collector loads (470 ohm + LED). The LEDs blink in opposition as each side alternately switches."
  },
